user_prompt: Suppose that a trendel, a laxum, and a doffen are candidates for Best Ploggel at the National Zorple Championship. Since these are the only contenders, if the laxum doesn’t win Best Ploggel, then if the trendel doesn’t win, the doffen will win. Moreover, the trendel likely will win Best Ploggel and hence the laxum likely won’t win. Does it follow that it’s likely that, if the trendel doesn’t win Best Ploggel, the doffen will?
